{"tid":695279,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【出口轉內銷，荒誕的歷史】","createTime":"2018-06-09T05:16:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-10T06:38:40.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7d5c7a227e2083ea642506229deba79653306cb4","tid":695279,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T05:16:29.000Z","msg":"六七十年代，許多香港人郵寄食物回大陸，接濟鄉間饑荒的親友，這是上一輩港人的集體回憶。然而，這些郵寄回鄉的食物究竟從哪裡來？卻是來自餓殍遍野的中國大陸。British Pathe這段影片，記錄了1961年「紅色中國」在大饑荒、許多人饑餓至死的時期，仍然出口大量食物賺外匯。而香港人卻真金白銀買食物寄回鄉，名副其實「出口轉內銷」。<br />\n<br />\n這不是抹黑，曾身在體制內的新華社資深記者楊繼繩，曾走訪全國調查，寫成紀實文學作品《墓碑》，還原六十年代大饑荒的歷史；其中，提到當年中國政府在糧食政策上，「對農民見死不救，繼續高徵購，繼續出口」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/620177918009590/videos/1932513460109356/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F620177918009590%2Fvideos%2F1932513460109356%2F&d=tBkfnkjO6ZWg6bX1Zt5ibB4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=996c2dea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/620177918009590/videos/1932513460109356/</a>"},{"pid":"321da3ca35e280822ffdb9c440eebc6d42bd135c","tid":695279,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T06:04:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b3a8273bc4a74984b56ef126e35820d8fba4ab","tid":695279,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T06:35:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe2cf6861c6404169405d625fd0bc40412d56b68","tid":695279,"uid":181162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T06:38:26.000Z","msg":"想發死人材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd40622195a54f97cf0ebf21f713ed3caf535ecc","tid":695279,"uid":181162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe2cf6861c6404169405d625fd0bc40412d56b68","tid":695279,"uid":181162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T06:38:26.000Z","msg":"想發死人